---
import TerminalWindow from './TerminalWindow.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 sm:px-8 border-t border-border">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-manager mb-3 text-center reveal">MANAGER SESSIONS</div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-3 reveal stagger-1">
      One agent manages the rest.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary text-center text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto mb-10 reveal stagger-2">
      A Claude session that reads your other sessions, sends them instructions, and reports back. Set it on a loop and walk away.
    </p>

    <!-- Ralph loops callout -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 reveal stagger-3">
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-manager/20">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-manager" style="animation: pulse-soft 2s infinite;"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-manager">RALPH LOOPS</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mb-3">
          Agent cron. Define a cadence and goals. The manager keeps your fleet moving.
        </p>
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-text-tertiary bg-bg-deep rounded-lg p-3 border border-border">
          <span class="text-secondary">"Every 30 min</span>, check for stalls. Restart with context. Ping me if something needs a decision."
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terminal demo -->
    <div class="reveal stagger-4">
      <TerminalWindow title="ralph" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm">
          <div><span class="text-manager font-bold">ralph:</span> <span class="text-text-secondary">Scheduled check — 3 workers</span></div>
          <div class="pt-1.5 border-t border-border mt-1.5"></div>
          <div><span class="text-success">auth-refactor</span> <span class="text-text-tertiary">·</span> <span class="text-success">running</span> <span class="text-text-tertiary">— 80% done</span></div>
          <div><span class="text-success">api-tests</span> <span class="text-text-tertiary">·</span> <span class="text-success">running</span> <span class="text-text-tertiary">— 12 passing</span></div>
          <div><span class="text-secondary">frontend-ui</span> <span class="text-text-tertiary">·</span> <span class="text-secondary">stalled 14m</span></div>
          <div class="pt-1.5 border-t border-border mt-1.5"></div>
          <div><span class="text-manager font-bold">ralph:</span> <span class="text-text-secondary">Restarted frontend-ui with fix context. Next check in 30m.</span></div>
        </div>
      </TerminalWindow>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
